				</ukm:Metadata><Primary><Body DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2007/3/body" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2007/3/body" NumberOfProvisions="1751" RestrictExtent="E+W+S+N.I." RestrictStartDate="2026-04-06"><Part DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2007/3/part/2" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2007/3/part/2" NumberOfProvisions="51" id="part-2" RestrictExtent="E+W+S+N.I." RestrictStartDate="2026-03-18"><Number><Strong>Part 2</Strong></Number><Title>Basic provisions</Title><Chapter DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2007/3/part/2/chapter/2" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2007/3/part/2/chapter/2" NumberOfProvisions="35" id="part-2-chapter-2" RestrictExtent="E+W+S+N.I." RestrictStartDate="2026-03-18"><Number>Chapter 2</Number><Title>Rates at which income tax is charged</Title><Pblock DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2007/3/part/2/chapter/2/crossheading/the-rates" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2007/3/part/2/chapter/2/crossheading/the-rates" NumberOfProvisions="9" id="part-2-chapter-2-crossheading-the-rates" RestrictExtent="E+W+S+N.I." RestrictStartDate="2026-03-18"><Title><Emphasis>The rates</Emphasis></Title><P1group RestrictStartDate="2026-03-18" RestrictExtent="E+W+S+N.I."><Title>The <Addition ChangeId="key-d43df9e231b084d5be9f098a9c4fcd2b-1568632740254" CommentaryRef="key-d43df9e231b084d5be9f098a9c4fcd2b">dividend nil rate,</Addition> dividend ordinary rate<Substitution ChangeId="key-3b5834e143feafeab6f32b33dfbbf148-1508425985405" CommentaryRef="key-3b5834e143feafeab6f32b33dfbbf148">, dividend upper rate and dividend additional rate</Substitution></Title><P1 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2007/3/section/8" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2007/3/section/8" id="section-8"><Pnumber PuncAfter="">8</Pnumber><P1para><P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2007/3/section/8/A1" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2007/3/section/8/A1" id="section-8-A1"><Pnumber><Addition ChangeId="key-be746fa1ef9babf3656539d7ef444409-1568214101689" CommentaryRef="key-be746fa1ef9babf3656539d7ef444409">A1</Addition></Pnumber><P2para><Text><Addition ChangeId="key-be746fa1ef9babf3656539d7ef444409-1568214101689" CommentaryRef="key-be746fa1ef9babf3656539d7ef444409">The dividend nil rate is 0%.</Addition></Text></P2para></P2><P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2007/3/section/8/1" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2007/3/section/8/1" id="section-8-1"><Pnumber>1</Pnumber><P2para><Text>The dividend ordinary rate is   <Substitution ChangeId="key-9be6ae45a5022f7c4b75d7f56416390a-1776700177590" CommentaryRef="key-9be6ae45a5022f7c4b75d7f56416390a">10.75%</Substitution>.</Text></P2para></P2><P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2007/3/section/8/2" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2007/3/section/8/2" id="section-8-2"><Pnumber>2</Pnumber><P2para><Text>The dividend upper rate is  <Substitution ChangeId="key-ea360ef5c4bf2168e1357984836a6875-1776700177590" CommentaryRef="key-ea360ef5c4bf2168e1357984836a6875">35.75%</Substitution>.</Text></P2para></P2><P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2007/3/section/8/3" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2007/3/section/8/3" id="section-8-3"><Pnumber><Addition ChangeId="key-0a21e6c3365bb41fba7112413f07785a-1508790160069" CommentaryRef="key-0a21e6c3365bb41fba7112413f07785a">3</Addition></Pnumber><P2para><Text><Addition ChangeId="key-0a21e6c3365bb41fba7112413f07785a-1508790160069" CommentaryRef="key-0a21e6c3365bb41fba7112413f07785a">The dividend additional rate is    </Addition><Addition ChangeId="key-0a21e6c3365bb41fba7112413f07785a-1508790160069" CommentaryRef="key-0a21e6c3365bb41fba7112413f07785a"><Substitution ChangeId="key-6403497eab64606d27c0a841effa12ab-1655912965484" CommentaryRef="key-6403497eab64606d27c0a841effa12ab">39.35%</Substitution></Addition><Addition ChangeId="key-0